For Linux/Mac
--------------
To run simulations in matlab with SCOTS you need compile the mexfile

1. set up the mex compiler in Matlab:

  >> mex -setup C++

2. edit the make file and adjust the variables (MATLABROOT) to match your Matlab installation.


3. Navigate to this (mexfiles) folder in a terminal and run

  $ make


For Windows
--------------

1. From inside MATLAB while you are in this (mexfiles) directory:

  >> mex -setup C++
  >> makewin